              "block_heading": "Patient Presentation",
              "block_type": "text",
              "data": "45-year-old male with hypertension (Amlor 10 mg) and iron deficiency (Ferose tab) presents with acute constipation (2 weeks), painful defecation, dry/hard stools."
            },
            {
              "block_heading": "Assessment",
              "block_type": "list",
              "data": ["Acute constipation (less than 3 weeks)", "Medications (CCBs, iron) may contribute"]
